<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Line indentation is currently done "by hand" for example in the console help system.</p>

<p>This could more easily be done with a ResponseDecorator that allows to specify the content option:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$response-&gt;appendContent("foo", array("indentation" =&gt; 8));
</code></pre>

<p>A patch for this decorator is appended.</p>

